<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n08048h"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08048h">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08048h"> 48(h)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> n&apos;est pas bizarre qui veut</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">L&apos;&eacute;criture bizarre n&apos;est pas souvent employ&eacute;e; c&apos;est qu&apos;il est plus facile de tracer un angle qu&apos;une forme &eacute;trange: <mark>n&apos;est pas bizarre qui veut</mark>. <br><font color="green">[Unusual handwritings are avoided; the reason is that it is much easier to trace an angle than a strange form: it is not so easy to be unusual.]</font> <small> J Cr&eacute;pieux-Jamin, <a name="JCJL" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#JCJL"><cite title="source">Les &eacute;l&eacute;ments de l'&eacute;criture des canailles</cite></a> (1923) 277</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
